0%26amp%3B%20Marsal%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20traditional%20resilience%20of%20summer%20travel%20demand%2C%20the%20winter%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20bigger%20risk%20than%20the%20peak%20summer%20period%2C%20and%20I%20expect%20airline%20management%20teams%20to%20consider%20post-peak%20summer%20capacity%20plans%20carefully%20given%20elevated%20demand%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%20uncertainties%20about%20tariffs%20and%20an%20increased%20rate%20for%20China%20again%20upset%20traders%20as%20the%20market%20slumped%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20dipped%203.5%25%2C%20while%20the%20Big%20Four%20airline%20stocks%20dropped%20between%2010%25%20and%2014%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20major%20swings%20seen%20last%20week%2C%20airline%20stocks%20have%20broadly%20plummeted%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%20shares%20went%20up%20nearly%20150%25%20last%20year%2C%20but%20it%20is%20down%20by%20a%20third%20since%20the%20start%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20is%20also%20down%20a%20third%2C%20while%20American%20Airlines%20is%20down%2044%25.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-loved-about-southwest-is-officially-gone-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20undergoing%20an%20overhaul%20of%20its%20business%20model%2C%20is%20still%20down%20nearly%20a%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FnDaEH%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22US%20airline%20relative%20YTD%20stock%20performance%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22416%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pessimism%20is%20based%20on%20fears%20that%20fewer%20people%20will%20travel%20than%20initially%20