ntentional%20choices%20that%20keep%20my%20family%20at%20the%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20learned%20that%20balance%20isn't%20about%20achieving%20a%20perfect%2050%2F50%20split.%20It's%20about%20making%20sure%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverworked-years-until-child-realized-work-doesnt-care-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20doesn't%20always%20come%20first%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20about%20finding%20ways%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20in-between%20moments%3B%20those%20are%20the%20moments%20that%20matter.%20And%20while%20I%20can't%20quit%20the%20hustle%2C%20I%20can%20remind%20myself%20why%20I'm%20doing%20it%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEasing%20back%20into%20work%20after%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20my%20youngest%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20hardest%20transitions%20I've%20faced.%20But%20it's%20also%20been%20a%20reminder%20that%20success%20doesn't%20hinge%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-200k-give-them-financial-security-inflation-costs-survey-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20security%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20hanging%20on%20by%20a%20thread%20some%20days%2C%20but%20I%20always%20try%20to%20make%20time%20for%20my%20littles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter's%20words%20continue%20to%20echo%20in%20my%20mind%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20her%20childhood%20memories%20to%20be%20of%20parents%20who%20were%20always%20too%20busy%20to%20be%20there.%20I%20want%20her%20to%20remember%20that%20we%20worked%20hard%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20that%20we%20also%20made%20space%20for%20love%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20connection.%20That%20even%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20some%20pretty%20chaotic%20days%2C%20we%20chose%20each%20other%2C%20and%20we'll%20always%20choose%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-hard-provide-kids-missing-childhood-balance-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Ins