%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESoni%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20India%20and%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20in%202005%2C%20said%20he%20struggled%20to%20settle%20in%20Bengaluru.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20the%20work%20culture%20was%20intense%20in%20India%20compared%20to%20Silicon%20Valley's%20more%20holistic%20approach.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Punit%20Soni%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Suki%20AI%2C%20living%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20Bengaluru%2C%20India.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20in%202015%20as%20Flipkart's%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20I%20experienced%20a%20profound%20sense%20of%20displacement.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%20for%20my%20MBA%20in%202005.%20I%20worked%20at%20Google%20and%20Motorola%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20until%20taking%20on%20a%20new%20role%20at%20Flipkart%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20being%20born%20in%20India%2C%20my%20years%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Silicon%20Valley%20fundamentally%20altered%20my%20professional%20and%20cultural%20identity.%20I%20spoke%20Hindi%20with%20an%20Indian-American%20accent%20and%20my%20professional%20and%20social%20mannerisms%20felt%20foreign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20I%20embodied%20the%20classic%20immigrant%20experience%20of%20feeling%20like%20an%20outsider%20in%20both%20my%20homeland%20and%20adopted%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cfa64ae2-15d6-4e97-8fd3-987c5bde8857%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20moved%20into%20a%20tropical%20Silicon%20Valley%20in%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20to%20Bengaluru%20in%202015%2C%20I%20started%20my%20new%20position%20at%20Flipkart%20and%20had%20no%20set%20timeline%20of%20how%20long%20I%20would%20be%20back%20in%20India.%20I%20was%20excited%20for%20the%20job%20and%20to%20move%20when%20the%20country's%20tech%20scene%20was%20growing%20rapidly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20my%20family's%20relocation%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20find%20the%20right%20community.%20My%20wife%20had%20been%20to%20India%20before%2C%20but%20my%20children%20hadn't.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20chose%20Adarsh%20Palms%20in%20North%20Bengaluru%2C%20a%20luxury%20gated%20community.%20The%20neighhorhood%20had%20a%20predominantly%20expat%20population%20and%20offered%20a%20comfortable%20transition%20from%20California%20to%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELiving%20in%20a%20tropical%20replica%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20made%20our%20adaptation%20easier%2C%20providing%20a%20familiar%20environment%20for%20our%20family's%20social%20integration.%20Our%20children%20attended%20international%20schools%20with%20students%20from%20Sweden%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20convenient%2C%20this%20lifestyle%20came%20with%20a%20significant%20drawback.%20We%20were%20essentially%20living%20in%20a%20bubble%2C%20disconnected%20from%20local%20Indian%20society.%20Everyone%20socialized%20within%20the%20community.%20We%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other%20well%2C%20but%20sometimes%2C%20it%20could%20feel%20stifling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20a%20different%20environment%20than%20how%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20which%20was%20an%20open%20community%20with%20shared%20apartment%20complexes%20and%20kids%20running%20up%20and%20down%20the%20spaces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20excited%20to%20reconnect%20with%20old%20friends%2C%20but%20I'd%20come%20back%20to%20a%20sanitized%20version%20of%20India.%20I%20knew%20the%20language%20and%20culture%2C%20but%20it%20still%20felt%20unfamiliar.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20while%20settle%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20migrated%20to%20the%20States%2C%20I%20was%20a%20young%20immigrant%20student%20entering%20with%20few%20responsibilities%2C%20whereas%20moving%20to%20India%20in%20my%20adulthood%20involved%20constant%2C%20dramatic%20changes%20and%20a%20family%20to%20look%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20we%20missed%20opportunities%20for%20more%20authentic%20cultural%20immersion%2C%20particularly%20for%20our%20children.%20If%20we%20ever%20move%20back%2C%20I'll%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20more%20local%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d4fa91c-3f2a-45c1-aba2-372e78bbfd91%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20found%20the%20work%20culture%20is%20more%20intense%20in%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20work%20intensity%20in%20India%20presented%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Silicon%20Valley's%20professional%20environment.%20During%20my%20time%20working%20in%20Bengaluru%20between%202015%20and%202016%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20work-life%20balance%20was%20essentially%20nonexistent%20in%20the%20Indian%20tech%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20recognize%20certain%20growth%20phases%20demand%20intense%20effort%2C%20the%20cultural%20approach%20seemed%20to%20normalize%20continuous%20work%20to%20the%20point%20of%20potential%20burnout.%20Employees%20persevered%20through%20exhausting%20conditions%2C%20propelled%20by%20an%20extraordinary%20commitment%20to%20professional%20advancement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOffice%20dynamics%20in%20India%20were%20more%20complex%20than%20I'd%20experienced%20in%20the%20US%20with%20intricate%20political%20maneuvering.%20Indian%20colleagues%20would%20try%20to%20avoid%20saying%20%26quot%3Bno.%26quot%3B%20I%20think%20this%20stemmed%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20appear%20cooperative%20and%20avoid%20potential%20professional%20friction.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EWhereas%2C%20in%20American%20workplaces%2C%20there's%20more%20direct%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20positive%20side%2C%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20people%20I%20worked%20with%20in%20India%20was%20unmatched.%20The%20same%20work%20ethic%20and%20drive%20to%20succeed%20can%20found%20in%20small%20pockets%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20due%20to%20the%20competition%20in%20India%2C%20it%20was%20more%20widespread.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESilicon%20Valley%2C%20in%20comparison%2C%20marketed%20a%20more%20holistic%20work%20experience.%20With%20amenities%20like%20on-campus%20activities%2C%20wellness%20programs%2C%20and%20break%20rooms%2C%20tech%20companies%20attempted%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20that%20supported%20employee%20well-being.%20These%20benefits%20were%20exciting%2C%20but%20never%20a%20must-have%20for%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparing%20career%20growth%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20India%20is%20like%20comparing%20apples%20to%20oranges%3A%20they%20each%20have%20their%20advantages%20and%20drawbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20difference%20is%20that%20Silicon%20Valley%20has%20many%20tech%20companies%20and%20startup%20opportunities%2C%20whereas%20India's%20ecosystem%20was%20still%20developing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269e0abe6-2570-4a75-a9ab-6423e6ba6ca6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20Indian%20and%20US%20work%20culture%20is%20an%20advantage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20came%20back%20to%20the%20States%20and%20launched%20my%20own%20company%2C%20Suki%2C%20in%202017%2C%20but%20my%20personal%20connection%20remains%20deeply%20intertwined%20with%20both%20cultures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20still%20have%20family%20in%20India%20and%20Suki%20has%20an%20office%20there%2C%20so%20I%20make%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20visit%20and%20maintain%20my%20bicultural%20identity.%20Familiarity%20with%20both%20cultures%20helps%20me%20shape%20the%20tech%20ecosystems%20that%20I%20work%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20live%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20but%20I%20frequently%20return%20to%20India.%20I%20love%20being%20able%20to%20serve%20the%20country%20I%20was%20born%20in%2C%20while%20still%20paying%20my%20dues%20and%20loving%20the%20country%20that%20gave%20me%20my%20career%20livelihood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20At%20the%20core%2C%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20Indian%20tech%20cultures%20share%20a%20fundamental%20similarity%20of%20an%20intense%20desire%20to%20excel%2C%20innovate%2C%20and%20push%20boundaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Five-lived-in-silicon-valley-and-bengaluru-work-culture-differs-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744716411000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67fe36cac6ad288d147e28b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Five-lived-in-silicon-valley-and-bengaluru-work-culture-differs-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founder%20Punit%20Soni%20grew%20up%20in%20India%20and%20moved%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%20He%20returned%20to%20Bengaluru%20ten%20years%20later%20for%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Pooja%20Shah)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Five-lived-in-silicon-valley-and-bengaluru-work-culture-differs-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Man%20Facing%20Nearly%2030%20Criminal%20Cases%20Paraded%20By%20Police%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Police%20paraded%20a%20man%20in%20handcuffs%20in%20the%20Pune%20locality%20where%20he%20resides%20and%20urged%20local%20residents%20to%20come%20forward%20and%20file%20complaints%20without%20any%20fear%20against%20him%20in%20case%20they%20have%20been%20troubled%20by%20him%20or%20his%20associates.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744716088000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F202