hman%20year.%20None%20of%20my%20friends%20at%20other%20universities%20had%20holiday%20reading%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20read%20three%20times%20the%20equivalent%20of%20all%20the%20Latin%20and%20Ancient%20Greek%20I'd%20studied%20for%20my%20entire%20two-year%20A-level.%20My%20friends%20were%20out%20enjoying%20summer%20while%20I%20was%20stuck%20indoors%20reading%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-project-iliad-juiciest-highlights-ftc-prime-lawsuit-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHomer's%20%26quot%3BIliad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20intensified%20once%20I%20started%20my%20degree%20at%20Oxford.%20I'd%20compare%20my%20experience%20to%20my%20friends%20at%20other%20universities%2C%20who'd%20email%20me%20saying%20what%20fun%20they%20were%20having%20going%20out%2C%20partying%2C%20and%20socializing%20%E2%80%94%20in%20addition%20to%20their%20studies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20mostly%20stuck%20in%20my%20room%2C%20studying%20frantically%20in%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20relentless%20workload.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20feeling%20jealous%20of%20them%20and%20exhausted%20by%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20I%20was%20expected%20to%20read%20and%20translate%20Latin%20and%20Ancient%20Greek%20texts.%20I%20had%20very%20little%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-manager-lunch-every-day-month-better-work-life-balance-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ework-life%20balance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20robbed%20me%20of%20the%20joy%20I%20once%20felt%20studying%20these%20subjects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20myself%3A%20Do%20I%20want%20to%20be%20mostly%20holed%20up%20in%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fsmall-bedroom-hacks-that-save-space%5C%22%20