r%20concern.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20only%20going%20to%20get%20harder%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anurag%2C%20citing%20climate%20change%20and%20increased%20construction.%20Borewells%20aren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20due%20to%20the%20fragile%20terrain.%20Their%20home%20and%20Peoli%20rely%20on%20a%20nearby%20spring%2C%20supplemented%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354201%2Fhow-to-set-up-start-rainwater-harvesting-affordable-system-diy-steps-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tested%20and%20found%20to%20be%20cleaner%20than%20RO%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vasanthi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20spend%20a%20good%20part%20of%20my%20day%20switching%20pumps%20on%20and%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anurag%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20even%20reuse%20water%20from%20rinsing%20rice%20and%20vegetables%20to%20nourish%20their%20garden.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338048%2Fterrace-garden-tips-by-hyderabad-woman-grows-organic-vegetables-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWe%20grow%20only%20as%20much%20as%20our%20water%20supply%20permits%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20water%20in%20the%20spring.%20We%20may%20face%20a%20crisis%20in%20the%20summer%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Anurag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20the%20mountains%20really%20teach%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20the%20mountains%20tend%20to%20be%20self-sufficient.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20comfortable%20with%20your%20own%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anurag.%20Both%20being%20single%20children%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20developed%20hobbies%20that%20keep%20them%20engaged.%20%E2%80%9CI%20paint%2C%20do%20jigsaw%20puzzles%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vasanthi.%20%E2%80%9CAnurag%20is%20a%20reader%20and%20loves%20his